<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Djuseppeb | Progetti & Fanzine</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
            background: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 { margin: 0; color: #222; }
        .container { background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        
        section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
        h2 { border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff; padding-bottom: 10px; color: #007bff; }

        /* Griglia Progetti */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: #007bff; }

        /* Sezione Fanzine */
        .fanzine-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
        .fanzine-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .btn {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }
        .btn-read { background: #007bff; color: white; }
        .btn-download { border: 1px solid #007bff; color: #007bff; }
        
        footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; font-size: 0.8em; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Djuseppeb</h1>
    <p>Sviluppatore, Creativo & Autore di Fanzine</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
    
    <section id="progetti">
        <h2>I Miei Progetti</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Progetto 1</h3>
                <p>Breve descrizione del tuo progetto principale. Puoi spiegare cosa fa e quali tecnologie usa.</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/djuseppeb/tuo-repo">Vedi su GitHub →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Progetto 2</h3>
                <p>Un altro lavoro interessante che vuoi mettere in mostra nel tuo portfolio.</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/djuseppeb/altra-repo">Vedi su GitHub →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="fanzine">
        <h2>Archivio Fanzine</h2>
        <p>Sfoglia i numeri della mia fanzine. Clicca su "Leggi" per aprirla nel browser o "Scarica" per il PDF.</p>
        
        <ul class="fanzine-list">
            <li class="fanzine-item">
                <span><strong>Fanzine #40</strong> (Ultima uscita)</span>
                <div>
                    <a href="fanzine/numero40.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-read">Leggi</a>
                    <a href="fanzine/numero40.pdf" download class="btn btn-download">Scarica</a>
                </div>
            </li>
            
            <li class="fanzine-item">
                <span><strong>Fanzine #39</strong></span>
                <div>
                    <a href="fanzine/numero39.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-read">Leggi</a>
                    <a href="fanzine/numero39.pdf" download class="btn btn-download">Scarica</a>
                </div>
            </li>
            
            </ul>
    </section>

</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Djuseppeb - Creato con GitHub Pages</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>